<p>					Hemispherx BioPharmawww.hemispherx.net </p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p>Hemispherx Biopharma, Inc. (Hemispherx) is a specialty pharmaceutical  engaged in the clinical development of new drug therapies based on  natural immune system enhancing technologies for the treatment of viral  and immune based chronic disorders. The Company focuses on two core  pharmaceutical technology platforms Ampligen and Alferon N Injection. </p>
<p></p>
